overland route between kapoeta and torit and last weeks convoy 
was the first to make a new attempt 
mitchell said they will stop using the route again and any 
further supplies will be sent to torit through uganda 
the 132 million operation hopes to save 100000 lives in sudan 
where officials estimate as many as 500000 people died from 
drought flood and warinduced famine last year 
