the united states has received more than 1100 firsthand reports 
of sightings of live americans in 63 percent of the cases 
schneider says the americans had been in indochina but had 
returned home and are not missing in action twentyone percent 
were fabrications the other 16 percent are under continuing 
investigation 
can says some vietnamese people have been giving out false 
