characterization 
i have a clear conscience he says its true i had power 
but im proud to be able to say that it did not corrupt me if i 
had stolen millions of dollars i could live like a king in this 
country but obviously i dont live like a king believe me i was 
a soldier fighting for freedom not a politician interested in 
power and money 
